ğŸ“Š Sentiment Analyzer using DistilBERT
A web-based sentiment analysis tool built with Python, Gradio, Hugging Face Transformers, and Matplotlib.
Users can upload an Excel file (.xls/.xlsx) containing reviews, and the app will:

Classify each review as Positive or Negative
Display results in a tabular format
Generate a Pie Chart of overall sentiment distribution

